Object.Description:
A key which opens an entrance to the Magic Woods. The spirits of ancient heroes congregate in this enchanted glade.

Keys can only be used once you have 10 or more stars!

A powdery clump of dust harvested from the wings of a deceased fairy.
A staff constructed from the bark of trees exclusively found in the Magic Forest, charged with the lively spirits of legendary heroes.
An orb so potent in the art of dimensional magic that it can send opponents to different planes of reality for eons.
An unusual robe made out of strangely flexible wood and coated in an otherworldly tree sap.
A ring topped with a hardened piece of magical resin.

A key which opens a passage to the Secluded Thicket. Add flair here.

Keys can only be used once you have 10 or more stars!
